o translate the meaning of the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Waggle_dance\" title=\"Waggle dance\">waggle dance<\/a>. His theory, described in his 1927 book <i>Aus dem Leben der Bienen<\/i> (translated into English as <i>The Dancing Bees<\/i>), was disputed by other scientists and greeted with skepticism at the time. Only much later was it definitively proved to be an accurate theoretical analysis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Karl_Ritter_von_Frisch#cite_note-4\"><span>[<\/span>4<span>]<\/span><\/a><\/sup><\/p>","name":"Karl Ritter von Frisch","place_of_birth":"Vienna, Austria","place_of_death":"Munich ,  Germany","text":"Karl Ritter von Frisch ,  born in then Austria-Hungary, now Austria , Physiology or Medicine, 1973","year":1973.0}